| High | Require auth on `/users` before exposing PII | Email addresses are PII |
| Medium | Validate all path/query/body params (`express-validator` or `zod`) | Type confusion, injection defense |
| Medium | Rate limiting | Brute force / scraping defense |
| Medium | Graceful shutdown | Avoids dropped requests on deploy |
| Low | Replace `console.log` with `pino`/`winston` | Structured, auditable logs |
| Low | Explicit CORS policy via `cors` middleware | Makes intent reviewable |

