| A08 Software & Data Integrity | ✅ | No deserialization of untrusted data. |
| A10 SSRF | ✅ | No outbound HTTP based on user input. |
| Path traversal | ✅ | No `fs` or `res.sendFile` on user input. |
| Open redirect | ✅ | No `res.redirect` with user input. |
| Prototype pollution | ✅ | No merge/assign of untrusted objects. |

